# Avatar

`TxAvatar` displays a user image, brand mark, initials fallback, icon fallback, or custom slot content. `TxAvatarGroup` stacks avatar children, injects a shared size when needed, and renders a `+N` overflow avatar when `max` hides extra entries.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/avatar/src/types.ts`, `TxAvatar.vue`, `TxAvatarGroup.vue`, and `avatar.test.ts`.

